  "about_item": [
    "【Extra Large Size for Large/Medium Dogs】47\"L x 32\"W x 2.2\"Th extra large dog bed mat provides ample space for medium to large breed dogs (up to 90kg) to stretch out comfortably. Perfect grey pet mat for crates, kennels, carriers and pet houses, fits most standard extra large dog crates.",
    "【1600D Oxford Waterproof & Anti-Slip Design】Made of high-density 1600D Oxford cloth (tear/scratch/bite resistant) with full waterproof performance, effectively prevents pet urine, water, grass moisture from seeping. Non-slip bottom protects wood floors, couch, car seats from scratches and sliding, no more peculiar smell.",
    "【Durable & Comfortable PP Cotton Filling】Filled with soft, breathable and thick 3D PP cotton that is not easily deformed, offers a cozy resting spot for your pets. Refined reinforced stitching makes the pet camping bed more durable, suitable for long-term indoor/outdoor use.",
    "【Easy to Clean & Machine Washable】This kennel pad is fully machine washable/hand washable, small stains can be wiped clean with a wet towel or sprayed with a hose. Non-sticky pet hair design, dries quickly, saves your time on pet supplies cleaning.",
    "【Lightweight Foldable & Multi-Scene Use】Portable foldable dog mat can be rolled up with the included buckle, saves space and easy to carry. Ideal as outdoor camping dog bed, car travel pet mat, patio/deck rest mat, and indoor kennel pad for dogs, cats, rabbits and other pets."
  ],
